  <brief_title>Clinical Re-evaluation of Removing Blood Stasis Therapy in Treating Acute Cerebral Hemorrhage Safety and Efficacy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Clinical Re-evaluation of Removing Blood Stasis Therapy of Herbal Medicine in Treating Acute Cerebral Hemorrhage Safety</official_title>
